  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387450/extras/38ce7404dc14581fd344646b565d42f1.avif?t=1735006518\" width=616 height=135 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387450/extras/be4092f06ce67501ed913a10fdc769ba.poster.avif?t=1735006518\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387450/extras/be4092f06ce67501ed913a10fdc769ba.webm?t=1735006518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387450/extras/be4092f06ce67501ed913a10fdc769ba.mp4?t=1735006518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Choose event cards in each round to create a unique story.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387450/extras/5b12bb50e79340a80bf6ad58068b688e.avif?t=1735006518\" width=616 height=135 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387450/extras/1b003f7f046ac40979c09685f6e7480a.poster.avif?t=1735006518\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387450/extras/1b003f7f046ac40979c09685f6e7480a.webm?t=1735006518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387450/extras/1b003f7f046ac40979c09685f6e7480a.mp4?t=1735006518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The pages of the story are turned by you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_a